title: Black Lives Memorial Garden in Cal Anderson Park

communications.subject: Washington Public Records Act Request: Black Lives Memorial Garden in Cal Anderson Park
communications.communication:
To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the Washington Public Records Act, I hereby request the following records:

Any documents and communications related to the Black Lives Memorial Garden or Sun Bowl in Cal Anderson Park within the past two years
Any documents and communications related to turf renovation that affects the Black Lives Memorial Garden or Sun Bowl within the past two years
Any documents and communications related to the use of the land currently containing the Black Lives Memorial Garden or Sun Bowl within the past two years
Any documents and communications related to any park maintenance plans made within the past two years which will impact the Black Lives Memorial Garden or Sun Bowl

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes.

In the event that there are fees, I would be grateful if you would inform me of the total charges in advance of fulfilling my request. I would prefer the request filled electronically, by e-mail attachment if available or CD-ROM if not.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 5 business days, as the statute requires.

Sincerely,

Kathryn Spiers
